{"parse":{"title":"Al-Bayan (journal)","pageid":48081695,"revid":728945061,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p>\n<table class=\"infobox hproduct\" style=\"width:22em\"><caption class=\"fn\"><i>Al-Bay\u0101n</i></caption><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/File:Bayan,_1._Jahrgang,_1._Ausgabe,_Cover.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Bayan, 1. Jahrgang, 1. Ausgabe, Cover.jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/dc/Bayan%2C_1._Jahrgang%2C_1._Ausgabe%2C_Cover.jpg/180px-Bayan%2C_1._Jahrgang%2C_1._Ausgabe%2C_Cover.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"235\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/dc/Bayan%2C_1._Jahrgang%2C_1._Ausgabe%2C_Cover.jpg/270px-Bayan%2C_1._Jahrgang%2C_1._Ausgabe%2C_Cover.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/dc/Bayan%2C_1._Jahrgang%2C_1._Ausgabe%2C_Cover.jpg/360px-Bayan%2C_1._Jahrgang%2C_1._Ausgabe%2C_Cover.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"1333\" data-file-height=\"1741\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Editor</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Ibrahim_al-Yaziji\" title=\"Ibrahim al-Yaziji\">Ibrah\u012bm Al-Y\u0101zi\u01e7\u012b</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Categories</th><td>\nCulture, anthropology, language, education</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Frequency</th><td>\nOnce to twice per month</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Publisher</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Ibrahim_al-Yaziji\" title=\"Ibrahim al-Yaziji\">Ibrah\u012bm Al-Y\u0101zi\u01e7\u012b</a> and Bi\u0161\u0101ra Zalzal</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">First issue</th><td>\n1 March 1897</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Final issue</th><td>\n16 August 1898</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Country</th><td>\nEgypt</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Based in</th><td>\nCairo</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Language</th><td>\nArabic</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Website</th><td>\n<span class=\"url\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://nbn-resolving.de/urn:nbn:de:hbz:5:1-68616%20Al-Bay\u0101n\">nbn-resolving<wbr />.de<wbr />/urn:nbn:de:hbz:5:1-68616%20Al-Bay\u0101n</a></span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The Arabic periodical <i><b>al-Bay\u0101n</b></i> (English: \"announcement\" or \"declaration\") was published once or twice a month from 1 March 1897 until 16 August 1898. It was edited in <a href=\"/wiki/Cairo\" title=\"Cairo\">Cairo</a> by <a href=\"/wiki/Ibrahim_al-Yaziji\" title=\"Ibrahim al-Yaziji\">Ibrah\u012bm Al-Y\u0101zi\u01e7\u012b</a> (1847\u20131906)<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> and Bi\u0161\u0101ra Zalzal (1851\u20131905) and was the successor of the medical journal <i><a href=\"/wiki/At-Tabib_(magazine)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"At-Tabib (magazine)\">a\u1e6d-\u1e6cab\u012bb</a></i> (1884\u20131885). Since 1898, Al-Y\u0101zi\u01e7\u012b, a linguist and journalist from Lebanon, particularly built up his reputation as the chief editor of the journal <a href=\"/wiki/Ad-Diya\" title=\"Ad-Diya\"><i>a\u1e0d-\u1e0ciy\u0101\u02be</i></a> (1898-1906).<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Apart from scientific articles, al-Bay\u0101n focuses on cultural and anthropological topics such as language and education.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Al-Bayan_(journal)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">P\u00e8re Paul Soueid: Ibrahim Al-Yazigi, L'Homme et son \u0152uvre, Beirut 1969, pp.8-9.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">P\u00e8re Paul Soueid: Ibrahim Al-Yazigi, L'Homme et son \u0152uvre, Beirut 1969, pp.106-114.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">al-Bay\u0101n, 1st volume, 1st issue.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Further_reading\">Further reading</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Al-Bayan_(journal)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Further reading\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Ayalon, Ami (1995): <i>The Press in the Arab Middle East</i>, New York.</li>\n<li>Gla\u00df, Dagmar (2004): <i>Der al-Muqta\u1e6daf und seine \u00d6ffentlichkeit. Aufkl\u00e4rung, R\u00e4sonnement und Meinungsstreit in der fr\u00fchen arabischen Zeitschriftenkommunikation, Band I</i>, W\u00fcrzburg, pp. 42, 113.</li>\n<li>Hanna, Elias (1993): <i>La presse Arabe</i>, Paris.</li>\n<li>Hartmanns, Martin (1899): <i>The Arabic Press of Egypt</i>, London.</li>\n<li>Rugh, William A. (1979): <i>The Arab Press. News Media and Political Process in the Arab World</i>, New York.</li>\n<li>Soueid, P\u00e8re Paul (1969): <i>Ibrahim Al-Yazigi, L'Homme et son \u0152uvre</i>, Beirut.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Al-Bayan_(journal)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://nbn-resolving.de/urn:nbn:de:hbz:5:1